text: Edvinas Vaškelis (born June 20 1996 in Vilkaviškis, Lithuania) is a Lithuanian volleyball player who currently playing for Volleyball Bisons Bühl playing in Deutsche Volleyball-Bundesliga.Tinklininkas E. Vaškelis – geriausias Bundeslygos rungtynių žaidėjas In 2014 Vaškelis represented Lithuania in 2014 Summer Youth Olympics. == References == ==External links== * CEV profile * FIBV profile Category:1996 births Category:Lithuanian men's volleyball players Category:People from Vilkaviškis Category:Beach volleyball players at the 2014 Summer Youth Olympics Category:Living people
